              >POST</span
            >
            <code>/watermark</code>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-300">Add a text watermark to a video file</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-800/50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-700">
          <h3
            class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-purple-500"
